======================================================================
VERIFICATION SUMMARY
======================================================================

The ESP32-S3 to UCC21550 PWM interface with 51Ω + 33pF RC filter has been
verified for:

  ✓ Logic level threshold margins (VIH/VIL)
  ✓ Signal rise/fall times (<50ns target)
  ✓ Propagation delay characterization
  ✓ Frequency response (20-50kHz range)
  ✓ Noise immunity and EMI filtering
  ✓ Input loading within GPIO limits
  ✓ Duty cycle accuracy preservation

RC Filter Specifications:
  - Series resistance: 51Ω
  - Capacitance: 33pF
  - Corner frequency: ~94MHz
  - Purpose: EMI filtering, dampening reflections

Key Findings:
  - Excellent compatibility with 3.3V CMOS logic
  - Minimal impact on PWM timing (rise time increase <10ns)
  - Effective high-frequency noise rejection
  - Low GPIO loading (<1mA average)

Recommendations:
  - RC filter is recommended for production designs
  - Place filter components close to UCC21550 input pins
  - Use C0G/NP0 ceramic capacitor for temperature stability
  - Route signal traces away from switch node (high dV/dt)

